The US both imports and export oil depending on type of oil, refining capability and other factors.  See:
</p><p>
-- <a href="https://www.api.org/news-policy-and-issues/blog/2018/06/14/why-the-us-must-import-and-export-oil" title="api.org">Why the U.S. Must Import and Export Oil<span class="substr"> </span></a> [api.org] <br>
